name: Jamal (purple drank goon)
description: Jamal’s gDNA is the energy template of the chemical dextromethorphine hydrobromide - the main active ingredient in purple drank. When rapper Lil’ Wayne was 9 years old he got a cold, and unattended, accidentally drank enough cough syrup that Jamal sensed the energy and manifested in his room, making a deal w/ Wayne that upon continued use of sizzurp, he would acheive fame and fortune.
